Package: pdtools
Title: Tools to interact with NCBI's Pathogen Detection project
Version: 0.5.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Julian", "Trachsel", , "julestrachsel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2357-7737"))
Description: A collection of functions to help work with data from the ncbi pathogen detection project/database.
    Has functions for downloading the most recent metadata, cleaning metadata, downloading genome assemblies,
    and setting up and working with pangenomes.  
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: GPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
